review.description: This is probably the number one breakfast spot in this area I've been working here for 10 years they have a Starbucks a McDonald's and a Dunkin Donuts and I was very skeptical about trying out my breakfast from this cart. one morning so I finally did and I have to say I don't think I can start my morning without seeing this lady's beautiful face and running on her excellent coffee very friendly and great tasty breakfast sandwiches and man oh man the coffee is amazing amazingly delicious!!!!!
review.author: Kero D.
